k-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2020-11-Kenya-EU-funds_LONG_FINAL.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Embed of EU support for care reform for children in Kenya in the 2021\u20132027 period.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-15123355-37e5-4d56-8798-d5b132a5a804\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2020-11-Kenya-EU-funds_LONG_FINAL.pdf\">EU support for care reform for children in Kenya in the 2021\u20132027 period<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2020-11-Kenya-EU-funds_LONG_FINAL.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-15123355-37e5-4d56-8798-d5b132a5a804\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>With this paper, we call on key parties to ensure that the NDICI supports comprehensive childcare system reform in Kenya.\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5015,"template":"","tags":[30,71,25,40,51,80,7,70],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Call to Action: EU support for care reform for children in Kenya - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"With this paper, we call on key decision-makers to ensure that the NDICI supports comprehensive childcare system reform in Kenya.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/eu-support-for-care-reform-for-children-in-kenya-in-the-2021-2027-period\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Call to Action: EU support for care reform for children in Kenya - Hope and Homes\" \/>\n